TeamUp has carved out a strong position in the boutique fitness management space since its founding in 2012. Originally built for CrossFit boxes and yoga studios, the platform has evolved into a comprehensive solution handling everything from class scheduling to on-demand video delivery. In 2026, TeamUp competes directly with platforms like Wellness Living, Mariana Tek, and the lower tiers of Mindbody.

Our team evaluated TeamUp across eight boutique fitness locations—including cycling studios, HIIT gyms, and yoga spaces—over a six-month period to understand how it performs at scale. This review reflects real operator experience, not just feature checklists.

