**Hidden cost considerations:**

Payment processing fees apply separately through your chosen processor (typically 2.9% + $0.30 per transaction through Stripe). SMS messages beyond plan limits cost $0.02-$0.05 each depending on region. The white-label app on Pro plans requires Apple Developer and Google Play accounts ($99 and $25 annually, respectively).

At 10+ locations, TeamUp's per-location pricing becomes expensive compared to enterprise platforms offering flat-rate or member-based pricing. A 12-location operation on the Pro plan pays $4,188/month before processing fees—roughly equivalent to Mindbody's mid-tier enterprise pricing but with fewer advanced features.

